data.description: Welcome to this beautiful investment opportunity! This exceptional property presents a rare chance for investors seeking diverse revenue streams. The estate boasts two homes, each offering numerous upgrades, open floor plans, and enticing bonus rooms. The first residence is fitted with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, while the second home, an Accessory Dwelling Unit (ADU), offers 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms across a generous 2,100 square feet. Both residences are a must-see, promising limitless potential for rental income or a multi-generational family retreat. Nestled on an approximately 14-acre parcel, the property showcases a flourishing 4-year-old almond orchard that has been well-cared for. The orchard consistently produces a bountiful harvest, creating an additional revenue stream for the discerning investor. The property's water needs are secured by a recently installed 280ft deep AG well with dual drip lines, ensuring reliable irrigation. Furthermore, the property comes complete with essential equipment, including 2 tractors and 3 sheds! Don't let this exceptional opportunity slip through your fingers. Schedule a viewing today!
